# Build and Test

## Presets

- Windows: `cmake --preset vs2022` then `cmake --build --preset vs2022-release`
- macOS: `cmake --preset ninja-release` then `cmake --build --preset ninja-release`

## VST3 output (Windows)

`build/BackroomsMuffler_artefacts/Release/VST3/Backrooms Muffler.vst3`

Install to: `C:\Program Files\Common Files\VST3\`

## pluginval

```powershell
pluginval.exe --strictness-level 5 --skip-gui-tests --validate "<path-to-vst3>"
```

CI must fail when pluginval exit code ≠ 0.

## Formats

- Windows/Linux: VST3 + Standalone
- macOS: VST3 + AU + Standalone
